@RobGMacfarlane @EnvAgency Seriously, fines are not working and are not enough. 
Land simply needs to be taken away from people who are so abusive to it. 
I think that would stop this stuff happening pretty quickly.

@RobGMacfarlane @alicksimmons @EnvAgency EA do need to act, and the penalty needs to be severe!

Complete restoration to previous condition, and then forfeiture of the land would be about right!

Plus compensation for any land/property owners downstream if any damage occurs to their holdings!
